sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Home Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open home page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query active carousel slides
    DB-->>LW: Slides ordered by position
    LW-->>UI: Render welcome card and carousel

    User->>UI: Refresh / revisit page
    UI->>LW: New page request
    LW->>DB: Re-query active slides
    DB-->>LW: Latest slides
    LW-->>UI: Re-render home content
